snippet.title: Fish Royale - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Download on IOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/fish-royale-feeding-frenzy/id1504305327
Download on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appox.fish&hl=en

Eat or be eaten in this action-adventure game with puzzles to solve, secrets to find and epic bosses to defeat! You grow bigger for every fish you eat and you get new abilities and stats the more experience you get!

Fish Royale features:
- Simple and addictive gameplay: Eat smaller fish to grow bigger and stronger
- Play as different fish, like the playful dolphin, speedy seahorse or hardy turtle
- Upgrade your fish with new unique abilities and customize its stats
- See how long you last in the fish royale, where only the strongest survive
- Lot's of achievements to complete and items to find

Can you find the great white shark hidden deep in the ocean?
